-07T11:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間地點同你差唔多，可留TG傾傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你留，我加你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e399b6a8d1b1676ba57beacd9ae7fcb6b4366b0c","tid":146684,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"帶幾多避孕套同事後丸至夠？"},{"pid":"44bd5d00d2bb11f0d4d44c3c51f4a38f02ba6a18","tid":146684,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時間地點同你差唔多，可留TG傾傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你留，我加你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n驚自爆，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2483fe48edd45d0843464c1d5d605fb5e495cec1","tid":146684,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"帶套啦"},{"pid":"912ffeb336081413a947ef5ef35fab23cdc00251","tid":146684,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"唔好買火車證，因為限你某日數內用哂。<br />\n火車分開一段段買，只去官網，唔好去agent<br />\n越快買越平，最好比錢可以選埋位，因為真係好多人（睇路段）"},{"pid":"fcda1415f32c91fbacc187595352483d836fd57c","tid":146684,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"建議帶埋我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n論據如下：<br />\n1:可即時分享感受<br />\n2:增加互動空間<br />\n3:提供即時鼓勵推動嘗試新事物<br />\n4:人身安全受到保障<br />\n5:減少與當地居民溝通問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6:解決性需要</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c3c77676502b5370ab5cabbdbfa52ef622231e","tid":146684,"uid":83727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"我之前係波蘭生活過，有咩可以問下我。"},{"pid":"9ba9178aede9f7e9779061559be7e5410a26b147","tid":146684,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:15:57.000Z","msg":"畢直有幾多？邊到入邊到出？<br />\n<br />\n奧地利要去薩爾斯堡，國王湖同冰洞十分精彩<br />\n<br />\n德國建議去慕尼克玩古堡大道，柏林？不了。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭有6日，可以上波羅的海三國，或直衝俄羅斯既聖彼得堡。<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得只有羅馬比得上聖彼得堡，競技場book tour落地下層，十分精彩"},{"pid":"e594a373d02b0bb34977a5d9bc8f6a50cd881ff8","tid":146684,"uid":8628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"絲打，方唔方便留TG?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9475d9b4ea0013f291d3e5849492247608db561","tid":146684,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"火車唔一定方便過巴士，建議唔好買火車證，去到問下酒店/hostel火車定巴士方便。"},{"pid":"618138eda17c90f737892b0e37d3c49139f635dd","tid":146684,"uid":66227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"Hi <br />\nTg :hiauntie123"},{"pid":"d1eee0407248620c9d172b88b2bff1b0e182618b","tid":146684,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"波蘭至少都要去Warsaw Krakow. <br />\nCroatia 日子少就無謂去啦 因為個邊交通無咁方便 而且位處死角 逼你走回頭路<br />\n<br />\n舊年夏天去左東歐16國 有咩想知睇下我幫唔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038291ba818634ca2c8c5fee4385f5ff315dccc0","tid":146684,"uid":82818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"可以中間薩爾斯堡留兩三日入一入德國國王湖果頭，另外想波蘭之後順路可以去波羅的海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7240b069b0d8bb8986a5b01bfe2ac6844b57aa2","tid":146684,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"我23-30都係奧地利獨遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0f93357a22eee56d6dc7e142bd84626dd370f7","tid":146684,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":