sg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下krakow鹽礦3個鐘行唔行得晒？</blockquote><br />\n車程幾遠，可以行大約兩小時。</blockquote><br />\n去集中營仲多野睇<br />\n<br />\n另外budapest必去啦<br />\n維也納唔洗太多，是個好悶ge城市，一d都唔好玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前一日會去，第二日朝早就先鹽礦<br />\n諗緊買幾點火車飛去Warsaw<br />\n想問下火車飛可以提早幾多訂？而家仲未出到price <br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fceb889dd57dbc20f43c7884bbe82392860346ef","tid":146684,"uid":36813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"我無去波蘭<br />\n我vienna 去Salzburg 係坐westbahn 呢架火車<br />\n我果時仲要有特價&euro;20<br />\n基本上vienna 唔使太多日<br />\n兩三日已經足夠晒<br />\n<br />\nsalzburg 我去hallstatt 就係坐obb <br />\n早左超多係官網買<br />\n&euro;27 好似係<br />\n<br />\n由hallstatt 去ck <br />\n我為左方便<br />\n就坐ck shuttle <br />\npoint to point 直達 <br />\nczk900 <br />\n<br />\nck to prague 就坐student agency <br />\n又係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e8ec9dc990ef45508604678c225f67c64cde96","tid":146684,"uid":34665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"絲打，你波蘭去邊？"},{"pid":"9a3e67a16dd30ae80d268cf8da4ef2e665bfa8aa","tid":146684,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度係個行程，乜鬼車票都未買<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/180546_f94415147f918c7b288bd6122d0b7078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F180546_f94415147f918c7b288bd6122d0b7078.jpg&h=7d776820&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啪太多日，可以射去第2度"},{"pid":"09440f7f5b1c50c44ba434944c7dab4f56ac7f7e","tid":146684,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我無去波蘭<br />\n我vienna 去Salzburg 係坐westbahn 呢架火車<br />\n我果時仲要有特價&euro;20<br />\n基本上vienna 唔使太多日<br />\n兩三日已經足夠晒<br />\n<br />\nsalzburg 我去hallstatt 就係坐obb <br />\n早左超多係官網買<br />\n&euro;27 好似係<br />\n<br />\n由hallstatt 去ck <br />\n我為左方便<br />\n就坐ck shuttle <br />\npoint to point 直達 <br />\nczk900 <br />\n<br />\nck to prague 就坐student agency <br />\n又係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVienna去Salzburg 我都打算坐westbahn,但我上網睇佢話冇得訂，連價錢都冇<br />\nSalzburg 去Hallstatt 我打算坐巴士<br />\nHallstatt去ck我已經搵左車了，打算係bean shuttle訂"},{"pid":"20de44190d9de67abdf888e3df91fb90abcf97b9","tid":146684,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"Warsaw都必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我寧願去Krak&oacute;w + Gdansk."},{"pid":"df3df197a0be817d3f321974520320c2d6a9ad9b","tid":146684,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打，你波蘭去邊？</blockquote><br />\n都係Warsaw,krakow,Gdansk,Wroclaw"},{"pid":"6f870458e3bcd3e36fc1d4b4f3a0283999c7da7e","tid":146684,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Warsaw都必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我寧願去Krak&oacute;w + Gdansk.</blockquote><br />\n我會去曬，因為平<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2132c26f2a7e17fc88eb836bf370300d1adab76d","tid":146684,"uid":79185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:27:22.000Z","msg":"喺波蘭搭polskibus應該平過火車"},{"pid":"b7c31bd0ffb8a5822e37f91eb983e7ad87571d88","tid":146684,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我無去波蘭<br />\n我vienna 去Salzburg 係坐westbahn 呢架火車<br />\n我果時仲要有特價&euro;20<br />\n基本上vienna 唔使太多日<br />\n兩三日已經足夠晒<br />\n<br />\nsalzburg 我去hallstatt 就係坐obb <br />\n早左超多係官網買<br />\n&euro;27 好似係<br />\n<br />\n由hallstatt 去ck <br />\n我為左方便<br />\n就坐ck shuttle <br />\npoint to point 直達 <br />\nczk900 <br />\n<br />\nck to prague 就坐student agency <br />\n又係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nStudent agency 果架巴士堅係平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b303b77832d016a237fc4831d7976a6eed2640e3","tid":146684,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間地點同你差唔多，可留TG傾傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntg:lamurmother"},{"pid":"04f258bbc952ed975c867258325c595b149b709b","tid":146684,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁大個女準備第一次去歐洲，有朋友住維也納，但120%都係我自己一個岀發，所以買左來回機票<br />\n旅遊日子:4月3號-4月27號<br />\n買左中華航空3號岀發stop over 台北11個鐘，然後再去維也納<br />\n<br />\n我有2個問題<br />\n1.我plan到20號去完波蘭之後就唔知做乜好，定係我應該將成個行程拉長少少，定去多一個地方就返維也納9 hea<br />\n2.成個行程會經三個國家，屋企人係咁叫我買歐洲火車證，我應該買火車證/搭一兩程火車加shuttle bus 好？<br />\n<br />\n對我黎講最唔識解決嘅問題係交通，我睇到頭都爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw波蘭嗰幾日，我係大陸個app叫窮遊，搵到有個男仔又係去波蘭，同佢去好似仲危險國我自己去咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都仲考慮緊同唔同佢一齊去波蘭好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1提議絲打去波蘭之前可以考慮去埋德國<br />\n，Dresden Berlin 都順路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2其實Vienna 真係無乜野玩，可以排到臨走前先去都得<br />\n<br />\n3火車證其實唔抵， 分開買最好，有時有d時段會大減價，樓上有個巴打都講左<br />\n<br />\n去廿幾日咁多， 好葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251ecf3f6f3dee5b681976c99c567f7ba6928c71","tid":146684,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度係個行程，乜鬼車票都未買<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/180546_f94415147f918c7b288bd6122d0b7078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: